{"tid":961802,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好想喊點解心儀個女同事係咁樣樣","createTime":"2018-12-30T11:30:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-31T18:25:59.000Z","uid":157994,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8071e7866f529ab273f74ba5b6e279974c5ea347","tid":961802,"uid":157994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T11:30:51.000Z","msg":"事緣係咁既...<br />\n<br />\n尋日終於約到自己暗戀左好耐既女同事出街<br />\n行行下街見口渴就買左杯天仁飲<br />\n女同事見到笑我：「係飲就飲喜茶啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n跟住我答佢話未飲過<br />\n點知佢用勁不可置信既眼神望住我<br />\n仲串我話：「睇你鄉下仔未出過城咁，你快d去飲返杯先再同我講野啦」<br />\n我咪答係呀？下次飲下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁樣hea答<br />\n<br />\n雖然明知佢講笑 但係feel到之後睇戲同食飯都少左講野同多左隔膜，估唔到佢竟然中意飲喜茶，仲一副洋洋得意咁樣......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實而家d大陸野係咪真係hit到咁？我見連老母同d街坊成日買miniso，明明畢嬲去開日本城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"027f9e42689c49d3385a87d7d3784419db271e28","tid":961802,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T11:31:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3fd0209c9d1af945e1ad4bd24c2cf69cf92071dc","tid":961802,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T11:48:49.000Z","msg":"典解的人咁無自主-.-多兵大晒牙&gt;灬&lt;"},{"pid":"56de3f94e578094d7cf057609b6913292e62e113","tid":961802,"uid":207425,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T11:52:47.000Z","msg":"但天仁茗茶真係唔好飲。我有quota 都唔會飲天仁茗茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94bf5abfab09523d2e92d5c0bfb1c230a5a64a76","tid":961802,"uid":157994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56de3f94e578094d7cf057609b6913292e62e113","tid":961802,"uid":207425,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T11:52:47.000Z","msg":"但天仁茗茶真係唔好飲。我有quota 都唔會飲天仁茗茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gi